| parameter | description |
| --- | --- |
| type | block directive |
| path | `directives/builtins.js` |
| description | colored block used to highlight information |
| `.info` | blue informational (default) |
| `.warn` | yellow warning |
| `.danger` | red danger |
| `.ok` | green success |

