## `@row`
@divider

| parameter | description |
| --- | --- |
| type | block directive |
| path | `directives/builtins.js` |
| description | responsive grid whose columns are sized by the number of block directive children |
| note | warns at build time if it has no block directive children |

@demo
@row
  @card
    ðŸ¡¸ I'm on the left!
  @end card
  @card .right
    I'm on the right. ðŸ¡º
  @end card
@end row
@end demo

@callout .warn
The content in a row is responsive, so on smaller screens the columns may stack vertically instead of horizontally.
@end callout
@end card

